All of blocks have their own direct item forms. Blocks with numeric ID over 255 have item form with numeric ID of {{code|255 - (block ID)}} to avoid block item IDs being overlapped into the other item ID space.

The item IDs are the IDs of the block's direct item form, which is used in savegame files and addons. This may, in some cases (e.g. Bed and Sugar Cane) differ from the ID of the item used to place the block, attainable through normal gameplay, the Creative inventory, or the {{command|give}} command.
